{"meta": {"centerNodeId": "taxonomy-species-geospiza-conirostris", "centerNodeType": "taxonomy", "generatedAt": "2026-05-26T12:20:42", "includedNodeCount": 3, "includedLinkCount": 2, "layoutMode": "precomputed-static"}, "center": {"id": "taxonomy-species-geospiza-conirostris", "name": "大仙人掌地雀", "type": "taxonomy"}, "nodes": [{"id": "bird-大仙人掌地雀-9cafc5c3", "name": "大仙人掌地雀", "englishName": "Española cactus finch", "latinName": "Geospiza conirostris", "type": "bird", "status": "VU", "summary": "大仙人掌地雀（学名：Geospiza conirostris）是一种属于达尔文雀的鸣禽。 伊斯帕尼奥拉岛上的大仙人掌地雀的喙比Genovesa岛上的大仙人掌地雀大。在伊斯帕尼奥拉岛上它是喙最大的鸟，因此占据了勇地雀和大嘴地雀之间的生态位。 雌鸟的喙是红色的，羽毛是白色、棕色的，带有黑色。雄鸟的喙颜色比较深，羽毛是黑色的。大仙人掌地雀长而有力的喙特别适于吃种子和昆虫。大仙人掌地雀的食物包括种子、水果、仙人掌的花和偶尔也吃昆虫。它们在伊斯帕尼奥拉岛、Genovesa岛和达尔文岛上有分布，往往栖息在仙人掌上。 参考文献", "shortSummary": "大仙人掌地雀（学名：Geospiza conirostris）是一种属于达尔文雀的鸣禽。 伊斯帕尼奥拉岛上的大仙人掌地雀的喙比Genovesa岛上的大仙人掌地雀大。在伊斯帕尼奥拉岛上它是喙最大的鸟，因此占据了勇地雀和大嘴地雀之间的生态位。", "habitats": ["灌丛"], "imageUrl": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f3/Geospiza_conirostris_-Espanola_Island%2C_Galapagos%2C_Ecuador-8.jpg/960px-Geospiza_conirostris_-Espanola_Island%2C_Galapagos%2C_Ecuador-8.jpg", "kingdomId": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylumId": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "classId": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genusId": "taxonomy-genus-geospiza", "speciesId": "taxonomy-species-geospiza-conirostris", "taxonomyIds": {"kingdom": "taxonomy-kingdom-animalia", "phylum": "taxonomy-phylum-chordata", "class": "taxonomy-class-aves", "genus": "taxonomy-genus-geospiza", "species": "taxonomy-species-geospiza-conirostris"}, "expandable": true, "x": -62.52, "y": 29.1, "z": -368.52}, {"id": "taxonomy-species-geospiza-conirostris", "name": "大仙人掌地雀", "latinName": "Geospiza conirostris", "type": "taxonomy", "taxonomyLevel": "species", "summary": "大仙人掌地雀（Geospiza conirostris）是图谱中的分类级分类节点，当前关联1种鸟类，如大仙人掌地雀。", "expandable": true, "memberCount": 1, "x": -62.52, "y": 29.1, "z": -369.32}, {"id": "taxonomy-genus-geospiza", "name": "Geospiza", "latinName": "Geospiza", "type